URL for the iDevBlogADay article discussing this project:

http://www.learn-cocos2d.com/2012/12/ways-scrolling-cocos2d-explained/

This project includes 4 demos for the four ways you can create a cocos2d scrolling view:
- "Fake" scrolling
- CCCamera scrolling
- CCFollow scrolling
- Manual (CCFollow subclass) scrolling

Cocos2D version used:
	cocos2d-iphone v2.1 beta 2
